{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-docs-js","path":"/docs/with-remote-m2.html","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<p>While using this setup:</p>\n<ol>\n<li>ScandiPWA theme is run by <code class=\"gatsby-code-text\">wepack-dev-server</code></li>\n<li>All <code class=\"gatsby-code-text\">/graphql</code> requests are sent to your remote server</li>\n<li>There is an Nginx routing the requests</li>\n</ol>\n<blockquote>\n<p><strong>Note</strong>:</p>\n<p>it is impossible to test the website in production mode (of the webpack build). This is the main downside of this approach.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote>\n<p><strong>Note</strong>:</p>\n<p>the <code class=\"gatsby-code-text\">https://scandipwa.local</code> wont be available. The PWA features will not function.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<hr>\n<p>In code examples, you might stumble across such declaration:</p>\n<div\n              class=\"gatsby-code-button-container\"\n              data-toaster-id=\"95404250796026990000\"\n              data-toaster-class=\"gatsby-code-button-toaster customToasterClass\"\n              data-toaster-text-class=\"gatsby-code-button-toaster-text customToasterTextClass\"\n              data-toaster-text=\"Copied\"\n              data-toaster-duration=\"3500\"\n              onClick=\"copyToClipboard(`# to clone the fork\ngit clone git@github.com:<YOUR GITHUB USERNAME>/scandipwa-base.git`, `95404250796026990000`)\"\n            >\n              <div\n                class=\"gatsby-code-button customButtonClass\"\n                data-tooltip=\"\"\n              >\n                Copy<svg class=\"gatsby-code-button-icon\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path fill=\"none\" d=\"M0 0h24v24H0V0z\"/><path d=\"M16 1H2v16h2V3h12V1zm-1 4l6 6v12H6V5h9zm-1 7h5.5L14 6.5V12z\"/></svg>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"gatsby-code-bash\"><code class=\"gatsby-code-bash\"><span class=\"token comment\"># to clone the fork</span>\n<span class=\"token function\">git</span> clone git@github.com:<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>YOUR GITHUB USERNAME<span class=\"token operator\">></span>/scandipwa-base.git</code></pre></div>\n<blockquote>\n<p><strong>Note</strong>:</p>\n<p>the <code class=\"gatsby-code-text\">&lt;YOUR GITHUB USERNAME&gt;</code> is not a literal text to keep, but the “template” to replace with the real value.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"before-you-start\"><a href=\"#before-you-start\" aria-hidden class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Before you start</h2>\n<ol>\n<li>\n<p>If you plan to make changes to the theme make sure to <a href=\"https://github.com/join\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">create GitHub account</a>, or <a href=\"https://github.com/login\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">sign in</a> into existing one.</p>\n<ol>\n<li>Make sure you have a SSH key assigned to your GitHub account, and you current machine has the same key. Read <a href=\"https://help.github.com/en/github/authenticating-to-github/adding-a-new-ssh-key-to-your-github-account\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">how to setup SSH key on GitHub</a>.</li>\n<li>Make sure to fork <a href=\"https://github.com/scandipwa/base-theme\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\"><code class=\"gatsby-code-text\">scandipwa-base</code> repository</a>. Read <a href=\"https://help.github.com/en/github/getting-started-with-github/fork-a-repo\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">how to fork repository on GitHub</a>.</li>\n</ol>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Make sure your remote server has ScandiPWA installed on it</p>\n<p>The Magento theme could be different, but ScandiPWA modules should be installed and enabled. Read more how to install the ScandiPWA on existing Magento 2 server <a href=\"/docs/on-existing-m2.html\">here</a>.</p>\n<p>In case you do not have the ScandiPWA instance yet, try completing this setup using our instances: <code class=\"gatsby-code-text\">demo.scandipwa.com</code> or <code class=\"gatsby-code-text\">scandipwapmrev.indvp.com</code>. You can also request your own cloud instance by composing a mail to hello@scandipwa.com.</p>\n</li>\n<li>Make sure you have <code class=\"gatsby-code-text\">node</code> available on you machine. To test this, run:</li>\n</ol>\n<div\n              class=\"gatsby-code-button-container\"\n              data-toaster-id=\"38646497205017050000\"\n              data-toaster-class=\"gatsby-code-button-toaster customToasterClass\"\n              data-toaster-text-class=\"gatsby-code-button-toaster-text customToasterTextClass\"\n              data-toaster-text=\"Copied\"\n              data-toaster-duration=\"3500\"\n              onClick=\"copyToClipboard(`node -v # should be 10^`, `38646497205017050000`)\"\n            >\n              <div\n                class=\"gatsby-code-button customButtonClass\"\n                data-tooltip=\"\"\n              >\n                Copy<svg class=\"gatsby-code-button-icon\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path fill=\"none\" d=\"M0 0h24v24H0V0z\"/><path d=\"M16 1H2v16h2V3h12V1zm-1 4l6 6v12H6V5h9zm-1 7h5.5L14 6.5V12z\"/></svg>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"gatsby-code-bash\"><code class=\"gatsby-code-bash\">node -v <span class=\"token comment\"># should be 10^</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>In case this command resulted in error, install node using the <a href=\"https://nodejs.org/en/download/package-manager/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">official guide</a>. Prefer <code class=\"gatsby-code-text\">nvm</code> installation to get NODE version 10 specifically.</p>\n<h2 id=\"time-to-decide---core-or-custom\"><a href=\"#time-to-decide---core-or-custom\" aria-hidden class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Time to decide - core or custom?</h2>\n<p>The theme can be developed in two modes - as contribution into core theme, or as custom theme development on top of core theme. Let’s review each one:</p>\n<h3 id=\"for-scandipwa-core-contribution\"><a href=\"#for-scandipwa-core-contribution\" aria-hidden class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>For ScandiPWA core contribution</h3>\n<ol>\n<li>Get the copy of <code class=\"gatsby-code-text\">base-theme</code> - clone your fork, or clone the original repository.</li>\n</ol>\n<div\n              class=\"gatsby-code-button-container\"\n              data-toaster-id=\"74562921011734510000\"\n              data-toaster-class=\"gatsby-code-button-toaster customToasterClass\"\n              data-toaster-text-class=\"gatsby-code-button-toaster-text customToasterTextClass\"\n              data-toaster-text=\"Copied\"\n              data-toaster-duration=\"3500\"\n              onClick=\"copyToClipboard(`# to clone the fork\ngit clone git@github.com:<YOUR GITHUB USERNAME>/base-theme.git\n\n# to clone the original repository\ngit clone git@github.com:scandipwa/base-theme.git\n\n# to clone via HTTPS (not recommended)\ngit clone https://github.com/scandipwa/base-theme.git`, `74562921011734510000`)\"\n            >\n              <div\n                class=\"gatsby-code-button customButtonClass\"\n                data-tooltip=\"\"\n              >\n                Copy<svg class=\"gatsby-code-button-icon\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path fill=\"none\" d=\"M0 0h24v24H0V0z\"/><path d=\"M16 1H2v16h2V3h12V1zm-1 4l6 6v12H6V5h9zm-1 7h5.5L14 6.5V12z\"/></svg>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"gatsby-code-bash\"><code class=\"gatsby-code-bash\"><span class=\"token comment\"># to clone the fork</span>\n<span class=\"token function\">git</span> clone git@github.com:<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>YOUR GITHUB USERNAME<span class=\"token operator\">></span>/base-theme.git\n\n<span class=\"token comment\"># to clone the original repository</span>\n<span class=\"token function\">git</span> clone git@github.com:scandipwa/base-theme.git\n\n<span class=\"token comment\"># to clone via HTTPS (not recommended)</span>\n<span class=\"token function\">git</span> clone https://github.com/scandipwa/base-theme.git</code></pre></div>\n<blockquote>\n<p><strong>Note</strong>:</p>\n<p>sometimes, after the repository is cloned, the git chooses the <code class=\"gatsby-code-text\">master</code> branch as default. This is the legacy (incorrect) default branch in case of <code class=\"gatsby-code-text\">base-theme</code>. Please make sure you are using <code class=\"gatsby-code-text\">3.x-stable</code>. You can do it using following command:</p>\n</blockquote>\n<div\n              class=\"gatsby-code-button-container\"\n              data-toaster-id=\"61047902716180610000\"\n              data-toaster-class=\"gatsby-code-button-toaster customToasterClass\"\n              data-toaster-text-class=\"gatsby-code-button-toaster-text customToasterTextClass\"\n              data-toaster-text=\"Copied\"\n              data-toaster-duration=\"3500\"\n              onClick=\"copyToClipboard(`git status # expected output \\`On branch 3.x-stable\\``, `61047902716180610000`)\"\n            >\n              <div\n                class=\"gatsby-code-button customButtonClass\"\n                data-tooltip=\"\"\n              >\n                Copy<svg class=\"gatsby-code-button-icon\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path fill=\"none\" d=\"M0 0h24v24H0V0z\"/><path d=\"M16 1H2v16h2V3h12V1zm-1 4l6 6v12H6V5h9zm-1 7h5.5L14 6.5V12z\"/></svg>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"gatsby-code-bash\"><code class=\"gatsby-code-bash\"><span class=\"token function\">git</span> status <span class=\"token comment\"># expected output `On branch 3.x-stable`</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>If any other output has been returned, execute the following command to checkout the correct branch:</p>\n<div\n              class=\"gatsby-code-button-container\"\n              data-toaster-id=\"28834109542638543000\"\n              data-toaster-class=\"gatsby-code-button-toaster customToasterClass\"\n              data-toaster-text-class=\"gatsby-code-button-toaster-text customToasterTextClass\"\n              data-toaster-text=\"Copied\"\n              data-toaster-duration=\"3500\"\n              onClick=\"copyToClipboard(`git checkout 3.x-stable`, `28834109542638543000`)\"\n            >\n              <div\n                class=\"gatsby-code-button customButtonClass\"\n                data-tooltip=\"\"\n              >\n                Copy<svg class=\"gatsby-code-button-icon\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path fill=\"none\" d=\"M0 0h24v24H0V0z\"/><path d=\"M16 1H2v16h2V3h12V1zm-1 4l6 6v12H6V5h9zm-1 7h5.5L14 6.5V12z\"/></svg>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"gatsby-code-bash\"><code class=\"gatsby-code-bash\"><span class=\"token function\">git</span> checkout <span class=\"token number\">3</span>.x-stable</code></pre></div>\n<p>Later, for development purposes any new branch created from <code class=\"gatsby-code-text\">3.x-stable</code> can be used.</p>\n<ol start=\"2\">\n<li>Add following key to <code class=\"gatsby-code-text\">package.json</code>:</li>\n</ol>\n<div\n              class=\"gatsby-code-button-container\"\n              data-toaster-id=\"98353793393775970000\"\n              data-toaster-class=\"gatsby-code-button-toaster customToasterClass\"\n              data-toaster-text-class=\"gatsby-code-button-toaster-text customToasterTextClass\"\n              data-toaster-text=\"Copied\"\n              data-toaster-duration=\"3500\"\n              onClick=\"copyToClipboard(`{\n    // ...\n    &quot;proxy&quot;: &quot;https://demo.scandipwa.com&quot;\n}`, `98353793393775970000`)\"\n            >\n              <div\n                class=\"gatsby-code-button customButtonClass\"\n                data-tooltip=\"\"\n              >\n                Copy<svg class=\"gatsby-code-button-icon\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path fill=\"none\" d=\"M0 0h24v24H0V0z\"/><path d=\"M16 1H2v16h2V3h12V1zm-1 4l6 6v12H6V5h9zm-1 7h5.5L14 6.5V12z\"/></svg>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"gatsby-code-bash\"><code class=\"gatsby-code-bash\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    // <span class=\"token punctuation\">..</span>.\n    <span class=\"token string\">\"proxy\"</span><span class=\"token builtin class-name\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"https://demo.scandipwa.com\"</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<blockquote>\n<p><strong>Note</strong>:</p>\n<p>Do not commit this change, if planning to use with docker.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<ol start=\"3\">\n<li>From the cloned theme folder, execute following:</li>\n</ol>\n<div\n              class=\"gatsby-code-button-container\"\n              data-toaster-id=\"95054426850239230000\"\n              data-toaster-class=\"gatsby-code-button-toaster customToasterClass\"\n              data-toaster-text-class=\"gatsby-code-button-toaster-text customToasterTextClass\"\n              data-toaster-text=\"Copied\"\n              data-toaster-duration=\"3500\"\n              onClick=\"copyToClipboard(`npm ci # install dependencies\nnpm run watch-core`, `95054426850239230000`)\"\n            >\n              <div\n                class=\"gatsby-code-button customButtonClass\"\n                data-tooltip=\"\"\n              >\n                Copy<svg class=\"gatsby-code-button-icon\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path fill=\"none\" d=\"M0 0h24v24H0V0z\"/><path d=\"M16 1H2v16h2V3h12V1zm-1 4l6 6v12H6V5h9zm-1 7h5.5L14 6.5V12z\"/></svg>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"gatsby-code-bash\"><code class=\"gatsby-code-bash\"><span class=\"token function\">npm</span> ci <span class=\"token comment\"># install dependencies</span>\n<span class=\"token function\">npm</span> run watch-core</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"for-custom-theme-development\"><a href=\"#for-custom-theme-development\" aria-hidden class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>For custom theme development</h3>\n<blockquote>\n<p><strong>Note</strong>:</p>\n<p>initial setup must happen on real instance. After the bootstrapped theme is committed to the repository, you can proceed with this installation.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<ol>\n<li>Inside, clone your already bootstrapped <code class=\"gatsby-code-text\">scandipwa-base</code> package with theme already bootstrapped. The theme file should be present in <code class=\"gatsby-code-text\">&lt;REPO SOURCE&gt;/src/app/design/frontend/&lt;VENDOR&gt;/&lt;THEME&gt;/</code>.</li>\n</ol>\n<div\n              class=\"gatsby-code-button-container\"\n              data-toaster-id=\"17819986818003763000\"\n              data-toaster-class=\"gatsby-code-button-toaster customToasterClass\"\n              data-toaster-text-class=\"gatsby-code-button-toaster-text customToasterTextClass\"\n              data-toaster-text=\"Copied\"\n              data-toaster-duration=\"3500\"\n              onClick=\"copyToClipboard(`git clone <CUSTOM THEME REPOSITORY GIT REMOTE>`, `17819986818003763000`)\"\n            >\n              <div\n                class=\"gatsby-code-button customButtonClass\"\n                data-tooltip=\"\"\n              >\n                Copy<svg class=\"gatsby-code-button-icon\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path fill=\"none\" d=\"M0 0h24v24H0V0z\"/><path d=\"M16 1H2v16h2V3h12V1zm-1 4l6 6v12H6V5h9zm-1 7h5.5L14 6.5V12z\"/></svg>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"gatsby-code-bash\"><code class=\"gatsby-code-bash\"><span class=\"token function\">git</span> clone <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>CUSTOM THEME REPOSITORY GIT REMOTE<span class=\"token operator\">></span></code></pre></div>\n<ol start=\"2\">\n<li>Then, get matching <code class=\"gatsby-code-text\">scandipwa/source</code> package version from <a href=\"https://github.com/scandipwa/base-theme\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">GitHub</a> (lookup the required version in <code class=\"gatsby-code-text\">src/composer.lock</code>, lookup <code class=\"gatsby-code-text\">scandipwa/source</code> package) and clone it to vendor folder. Make sure the folder is present.</li>\n</ol>\n<div\n              class=\"gatsby-code-button-container\"\n              data-toaster-id=\"54674518597205270000\"\n              data-toaster-class=\"gatsby-code-button-toaster customToasterClass\"\n              data-toaster-text-class=\"gatsby-code-button-toaster-text customToasterTextClass\"\n              data-toaster-text=\"Copied\"\n              data-toaster-duration=\"3500\"\n              onClick=\"copyToClipboard(`mkdir -p src/vendor/scandipwa/source\ngit clone git@github.com:scandipwa/base-theme.git src/vendor/scandipwa/source`, `54674518597205270000`)\"\n            >\n              <div\n                class=\"gatsby-code-button customButtonClass\"\n                data-tooltip=\"\"\n              >\n                Copy<svg class=\"gatsby-code-button-icon\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path fill=\"none\" d=\"M0 0h24v24H0V0z\"/><path d=\"M16 1H2v16h2V3h12V1zm-1 4l6 6v12H6V5h9zm-1 7h5.5L14 6.5V12z\"/></svg>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"gatsby-code-bash\"><code class=\"gatsby-code-bash\"><span class=\"token function\">mkdir</span> -p src/vendor/scandipwa/source\n<span class=\"token function\">git</span> clone git@github.com:scandipwa/base-theme.git src/vendor/scandipwa/source</code></pre></div>\n<ol start=\"3\">\n<li>Add following key to <code class=\"gatsby-code-text\">package.json</code>, located in your theme’s folder (<code class=\"gatsby-code-text\">&lt;REPO SOURCE&gt;/src/app/design/frontend/&lt;VENDOR&gt;/&lt;THEME&gt;/package.json</code>):</li>\n</ol>\n<div\n              class=\"gatsby-code-button-container\"\n              data-toaster-id=\"77050475931605730000\"\n              data-toaster-class=\"gatsby-code-button-toaster customToasterClass\"\n              data-toaster-text-class=\"gatsby-code-button-toaster-text customToasterTextClass\"\n              data-toaster-text=\"Copied\"\n              data-toaster-duration=\"3500\"\n              onClick=\"copyToClipboard(`{\n    // ...\n    &quot;proxy&quot;: &quot;https://demo.scandipwa.com&quot;\n}`, `77050475931605730000`)\"\n            >\n              <div\n                class=\"gatsby-code-button customButtonClass\"\n                data-tooltip=\"\"\n              >\n                Copy<svg class=\"gatsby-code-button-icon\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path fill=\"none\" d=\"M0 0h24v24H0V0z\"/><path d=\"M16 1H2v16h2V3h12V1zm-1 4l6 6v12H6V5h9zm-1 7h5.5L14 6.5V12z\"/></svg>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"gatsby-code-bash\"><code class=\"gatsby-code-bash\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    // <span class=\"token punctuation\">..</span>.\n    <span class=\"token string\">\"proxy\"</span><span class=\"token builtin class-name\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"https://demo.scandipwa.com\"</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<blockquote>\n<p><strong>Note</strong>:</p>\n<p>Do not commit this change, if planning to use with docker.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<ol start=\"4\">\n<li>From the custom theme theme folder, execute following:</li>\n</ol>\n<div\n              class=\"gatsby-code-button-container\"\n              data-toaster-id=\"15745573049856377000\"\n              data-toaster-class=\"gatsby-code-button-toaster customToasterClass\"\n              data-toaster-text-class=\"gatsby-code-button-toaster-text customToasterTextClass\"\n              data-toaster-text=\"Copied\"\n              data-toaster-duration=\"3500\"\n              onClick=\"copyToClipboard(`npm ci # install dependencies\nnpm run watch`, `15745573049856377000`)\"\n            >\n              <div\n                class=\"gatsby-code-button customButtonClass\"\n                data-tooltip=\"\"\n              >\n                Copy<svg class=\"gatsby-code-button-icon\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path fill=\"none\" d=\"M0 0h24v24H0V0z\"/><path d=\"M16 1H2v16h2V3h12V1zm-1 4l6 6v12H6V5h9zm-1 7h5.5L14 6.5V12z\"/></svg>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"gatsby-code-bash\"><code class=\"gatsby-code-bash\"><span class=\"token function\">npm</span> ci <span class=\"token comment\"># install dependencies</span>\n<span class=\"token function\">npm</span> run <span class=\"token function\">watch</span></code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"time-to-open-the-site\"><a href=\"#time-to-open-the-site\" aria-hidden class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Time to open the site</h2>\n<ol>\n<li>Open your favorite browser, i.e. Google Chrome</li>\n<li>Open un-secure <a href=\"localhost:3003l\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">localhost:3003</a> domain</li>\n</ol>\n<blockquote>\n<p><strong>Note</strong>:</p>\n<p>in case you are getting CORS issues printed out in console, make sure to run chrome with disabled web-security flag set.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"something-does-not-work\"><a href=\"#something-does-not-work\" aria-hidden class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Something does not work?</h2>\n<p>Follow this simple algorithm:</p>\n<ol>\n<li>Refer to the <a href=\"./development.html\">FAQ page</a>. It most probably already has the solution to your problem.</li>\n</ol>\n<blockquote>\n<p><strong>Note</strong>:</p>\n<p>the Docker setup related issues are also mentioned in this document.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<ol start=\"2\">\n<li>If the issue still persists, <a href=\"https://join.slack.com/t/scandipwa/shared_invite/enQtNzE2Mjg1Nzg3MTg5LTQwM2E2NmQ0NmQ2MzliMjVjYjQ1MTFiYWU5ODAyYTYyMGQzNWM3MDhkYzkyZGMxYTJlZWI1N2ExY2Q1MDMwMTk\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">join our community slack</a>, and feel free to ask questions in <code class=\"gatsby-code-text\">#pwa_tech</code> public channel.</li>\n<li>Alternatively <a href=\"https://github.com/scandipwa/scandipwa-base/issues/new/choose\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">create an issue on GitHub</a> - however, the response time there will be a little-bit longer than in community Slack.</li>\n</ol>","frontmatter":{"title":"Setting up the theme with remote M2 server"},"fields":{"path":"content/docs/with-remote-m2.md","slug":"/docs/with-remote-m2.html"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/docs/with-remote-m2.html"}},"staticQueryHashes":[]}